title: Golson's 3 touchdowns lead No. 12 Florida State to 41-21 win
text:
> Florida Golson's 3 touchdowns lead No. 12 Florida State to 41-21 win Florida State quarterback Everett Golson (6) scrambles in the second half of an NCAA college football game against Louisville in Tallahassee, Fla., Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015. Florida State defeated Louisville 41-21. (AP Photo/Mark Wallheiser) (AP Photo/Mark Wallheiser)
